metadata.name: Cowboy #1
metadata.description:
Cool Cowboys is a collection of 10,000 NFTs that are made up of hundreds of exciting visual and Hand - drawn traits designed by Mohamad.A and some traits are inspired from The Doodles NFT Collection.
Cool Cowboys are the guys who has been teleported to the west world by a sudden change that just happened in the Space Doodles World.
Now these Cool guys just want to discover joy and find their way in this wild world.
